<BaseLayout title="Amethyst Orblight" description="A violet glowing insect linked to Hearthcrest Callers.">
  <section class="page-section">
    <p class="eyebrow">World · Animals</p>
    <h1>Amethyst Orblight</h1>
    <p class="lede">A violet glowing insect whose soft hum gathers around Hearthcrest Callers during feeding windows.</p>

    <article class="visual-callout visual-callout-language">
      <div class="visual-callout-mark" aria-hidden="true"><span>●</span></div>
      <div class="visual-callout-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Insect symbiosis</p>
        <h2>Not decorative lights</h2>
        <p>Amethyst Orblights are small luminous insects linked to the Hearthcrest Caller’s feeding and breeding cycle. Their glow and hum are part of the ecology.</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>How to recognise it</h2>
      <p>An Amethyst Orblight appears as a small violet or amethyst glow with a darker centre, a soft orb-like body, a gentle pulsing edge, and slow group spirals near warmth.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Sound and movement</h2>
      <p>Amethyst Orblights make a low glassy hum with a soft pulsing buzz. The hum becomes steadier near a Hearthcrest Caller during feeding windows.</p>
      <p>They float in slow circles, then gather into loose spirals around crest warmth, mouth-light, warm feeding windows, dung nursery sites, and calm large-animal resting grounds.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>What it does in the world</h2>
      <p>Amethyst Orblights are part of a cycle involving Hearthcrest Caller crest warmth, mouth-light feeding windows, eggs, larvae, warm dung nurseries, and grassland renewal.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <h2>Related animals</h2>
      <div class="link-list">
        <a href="/world/animals/hearthcrest-caller/">Hearthcrest Caller</a>
        <a href="/world/animals/mosskeep-frog/">Mosskeep Frog</a>
        <a href="/world/animals/">Animals of Vaelinya</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">Accessibility note</p>
      <p>Amethyst Orblights are violet glowing insects whose soft hum gathers around Hearthcrest Callers during feeding windows.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
